{"tid":2100341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲：呼籲國民考慮留在香港的需要","createTime":"2020-07-09T03:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T04:15:19.000Z","uid":227801,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1846043e6d60d1ac36393276b90938d83d880ecd","tid":2100341,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"莫里森：暫停澳洲與香港的引渡協議<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫理森表示，關注香港實施《港區國安法》，宣布暫停執行澳洲與香港之間的引渡協議，又提出新的移民計劃，為香港人提供移民機會。即日起，延長正在澳洲的香港人逗留期限至5年，包括目前持有學生簽證和臨時工作簽證的人士，並提供途徑，讓他們成為澳洲永久居民。另外，澳洲更新對香港的旅遊警示，提示國民不要前往香港，又提醒在香港的澳洲公民和居民，在香港實施港區國安法後，被拘捕及遞解至中國內地的風險增加，呼籲他們重新考慮留在香港的需要。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-09 11:18:42 (2)"},{"pid":"593a4e5bccfba243171ac55092e820512e6250b1","tid":2100341,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380c4315fc53f7d53405e8fe6d3b785f7bde5d6a","tid":2100341,"uid":228868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港很危險 不要來"},{"pid":"582df95c1613b5602851ed4b115a862256a41a09","tid":2100341,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"澳洲，加拿大都話停就停<br />\n<br />\n美國仲考慮緊所謂2大絕招<br />\n1.停止引渡<br />\n2.停止同香港警察合作<br />\n<br />\n有可能搞死習近平<br />\n因為習近平 笑到爆血管<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433363e8d44967f93331ca87d05990e487efcb83","tid":2100341,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8165cae0888856bba03947200b752243bf04dc","tid":2100341,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"....如果撤僑就大撚獲"},{"pid":"327145304213b4b2c97ce26b4af5